      <abstract>
        <p>A new heterocycle, 2-[4-(hexadecyloxy)-3-methoxyphenyl]-1,3-benzothiazole, was prepared and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR, elemental analysis and MS spectroscopic data are reported.</p>
      </abstract>
